===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|poudre}}, {{m|enm|pouder}}, {{m|enm|pouldre}}, borrowed from {{der|en|fro|poudre}}, {{m|fro|poldre}}, {{m|fro|puldre}}, from {{der|en|la|pulverem}}, accusative singular of {{der|en|la|pulvis||dust, powder}}. compare [[pollen]] fine flour, mill dust, E. pollen. Compare [[polverine]], [[pulverize]].

